QuestData.Title: Tidal Sigil of Skwol
QuestData.Description: The sigils of the Abyssal High Council are crafted from the distilled essence of the element of their holder. This sigil was crafted from coral and smoothed by the tides.
QuestData.LogDescription: Bring the Tidal Sigil of Skwol to Field Marshal Snowfall in Silithus.
